# .cwshare - Files to copy to new worktrees.
#
# Listed paths are copied from the source worktree to the new one when you
# run `cw new`. Useful for local-only configs that aren't tracked in git.
#
# Format:
#   - One file/directory path per line (relative to repo root)
#   - Lines starting with # are comments
#   - Empty lines are ignored
#
# This repo currently has no untracked local config files to share.
